# to make use of supplied trip interval data
tripTibble |>
    
    dplyr::mutate("trip_time" = lubridate::time_length(
        lubridate::interval(started_at,
                            ended_at),
        unit = "minute"), 
        .keep = "all"
    ) |>
    arrow::write_dataset("tempFiles",
                         existing_data_behavior = "delete")
